items.title: Broken files because of git-lfs shenanigans
items.body:
Files like https://github.com/foone/BRender-v1.3.2/blob/main/lib/brdbwfrr.lib seems to have been eaten by the git-lfs part of github and cannot be checkout.

A `git lfs push` or something might be needed because standard git clone has just placeholders:
```
❯ cat lib/brdbmfr.lib
version https://git-lfs.github.com/spec/v1
oid sha256:48435d48bd2157c346bb5b3d1c24506e024f58a4f2c711527cd943c620a43054
size 138690
```
